open MeasureTheory Measure ProbabilityTheory unitInterval Sym2
open scoped Finset

namespace SimpleGraph
variable {V ╬ę : Type*} {m : MeasurableSpace ╬ę} {G H : ╬ę Ôćĺ SimpleGraph V} {eÔéü eÔéé : Sym2 V} {p q : I}
  {P : Measure ╬ę}

/-!
### Sigma-algebra on simple graphs

In this section, we pull back the sigma-algebra on `V Ôćĺ V Ôćĺ Prop` to a sigma-algebra on
`SimpleGraph V` and prove that common operations are measurable.

