So far, we have the definition of binomial random graphs. Now we need to prove the theorem about the union.

```tactics
lemma IsBinomialRandom.identDistrib_mem_edgeSet (hG : IsBinomialRandom G p P) :
    IdentDistrib (fun ¤ë ÔćŽ eÔéü Ôłł (G ¤ë).edgeSet) (fun ¤ë ÔćŽ eÔéé Ôłł (G ¤ë).edgeSet) P P := sorry
```

This lemma is not needed for the proof, so we can remove it.

Similarly for the other lemmas:
```tactics
